Debe Sylvester Ojukwu, the first son of late Biafran warlord Dim Chukwuemeka Odumekwu Ojukwu, is dead.
A family source, who confirmed the news to Vanguard, said he slumped and died at a private hospital in Lagos.
The family is yet to issue a statement on it.
Debe had had a problem with his sibling who had gone to court to deny the late warlord fathered him.
